{"tid":954985,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片： 女店員捉賊　硬食兜肚飛腳","createTime":"2018-12-25T05:13:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T05:19:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fc6eb3fea5250a95ce07bfec39d0a165d9c45403","tid":954985,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T05:13:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181225/20576414\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181225%2F20576414&d=SRlMtRg31rN53dMXQMtoogHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=4df66c7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181225%2F20576414&h=a2a63c5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181225/20576414</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年12月25日 <br />\n爆相爆片：<br />\n女店員捉賊　硬食兜肚飛腳<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181225/large/a1103a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181225%2Flarge%2Fa1103a.gif&h=b5735216&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n便利店女職員遭賊人踢傷腹部。<br />\n<br />\n「捉佢捉佢，報警！」將軍澳翠林商場一間便利店嘅女職員一路追一路嗌，讀者陳先生走上去了解同拍片。原來上周四下晝3點左右，一個女人喺便利店懷疑偷嘢，被女職員喝住，佢向女職員掟嘢仲伸咗對方個肚一腳，女職員追出，一個男途人幫手將佢女賊制服。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181225/large/a1103b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181225%2Flarge%2Fa1103b.gif&h=3bfc55f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女賊人遭制服後瞓地，被途人指摘。<br />\n<br />\n女賊被制服後一直瞓地下，男途人鬧佢：「你唔好扮儍呀！啲街坊俾你恰嘅咩？人哋喺度打工咋嘛，你打人做乜！」個女賊就話：「對唔住，我講sorry！」保安員都有埋去了解，在場人士報警。 <br />\n<br />\n警方表示，嗰個37歲姓廖嘅女人喺便利店偷咗一樽價值10蚊嘅鮮奶，同埋一本200蚊嘅雜誌之後走咗去，便利店54歲姓羅女職員追截，俾對方踢咗一腳，最後由途人制服賊人。廖女涉嫌盜竊同普通襲擊被捕。之後疑犯同女職員分別送院治理。  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片： 電動輪椅上斜着火　 伯伯險燒八月十五"},{"pid":"275b7b9b6d48f59d93c1df2ca1fb40de50279437","tid":954985,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T05:19:48.000Z","msg":"偷奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}